Package: sil-kit-adapter-tap
Architecture: any
Depends: libsilkit5(= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Attach the Vector SIL Kit to a TAP device
 The Vector SIL Kit Adapter for TAP devices is an open-source tool which
 provides first-class support for TAP devices of the host operating system.
 The SIL Kit Adapter TAP source and documentation is licensed under a
 permissible open source license, see LICENSE file. For licenses of third
 party dependencies, see ThirdParty/LICENSES.rst.
